==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Insistent
<hw>In*sist"ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>insistens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of
<ets>insistere</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Standing or resting on something; <as>as, an
<ex>insistent</ex> wall</as>.</def> <rj><au>Sir H. Wotton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Insisting; persistent; persevering.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>See <er>Incumbent</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Insistently</ent>⟦br⟧
